     @Transactional - Method level annotation.

2. Spring boot exception handilng.
     @RestControllerAdvice - class level annotation
     @ExceptionHandler - Method level annotation

3. Rest Endpoint communication.
   1. add spring webflux dependency
   2. We can use Webclient which is available in the above dependency to communicate with other server Rest endpoints.
     WebClient.builder().build()
                .get()
                .uri("https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/users")
                .retrieve()
                .bodyToMono(String.class)
                .block();
      get() - http method
      uri - URL we goinmg to hit to get response
      retrieve - execute the request
      bodyToMono - the response we received will be mapped to string type
      block - wait until the execution completes.

